* timeout
  If you want to shorten the time it takes for your job to hang
  (and fail), assign smallish numbers to ‘timeout’ and/or ‘maxSilent’
  in the ‘meta’ section.  ([[file:rcs/release.nix::timeout][RCS does this, for example.]])
